<AlertDialog phx-click="hideDialog">
      <ConfirmButton>
          <TextButton phx-click="hideDialog">
            <Text>Confirm</Text>
          </TextButton>
      </ConfirmButton>
      <DismissButton>
        <OutlinedButton phx-click="hideDialog">
          <Text>Dismiss</Text>
        </OutlinedButton>
      </DismissButton>
      <Icon imageVector="filled:Add"></Icon>
      <Title>Alert Title</Title>
      <Content>
          <Text>Alert message</Text>
      </Content>
    </AlertDialog>
